Ratu Luhur - A tale of Bravery

@fabienne_fng @missuniverse 

@naranaia_ for @jemberfashioncarnaval 

Mastermind @bubahalfian 

Photografer @mariophotographie video @yoyokpowel 

Costume by @fhanany_ivan @syamushad @aisyahisnainyy @dhana_bk @tonybambe and other 11 hand skilled artisant who work and collaborate collectively to create this masterpiece ❤️ on behalf of @naranaia_ @jemberfashioncarnaval we presents you not only cultural art costume but it’s also a story about journey of beauty within the strenght of Indonesian woman. Through good and bad times. Struggling to achieve her dreams through lot of obstacles. 
Last but not least I’d like to thanks to my management team who work hard to embodied my vision @rieckomara @wdyaoktvian @rickyrijkaard @natalia_fabsan @poppycapella_

 “Ratu Luhur”’s costume, carefully chosen colors represent Fabianne’s journey. From Black, symbolizing her darkest moments through a journey of finding her strenght from bullying, an gold representing the dignity and beauty within her heart, and copper reflecting her perseverance and resilience through every obstacle she faces.

This costume represent a journey of good vs evil. Fabianne will emit an unstoppable charm when wearing this costume to graces the Miss Universe stage. 
“Ratu Luhur” symbolizes empowerment for all women who have experienced bullying. The message is that by transforming negative views into sources of inspiration, we can bring forth bravery and unwavering strength within ourselves.
“Ratu Luhur” stands as a symbol for all women in Indonesia who stand strong against bullying and use insults as fuel to achieve success. Hopefully, this costume can inspire and motivate anyone who wears it and contribute to building a more compassionate and inclusive society in the future.

Dengan waktu yang sangat singkat @bubahalfian n tim buat National Costum sekeren ini, 🫡 hormat, @fhanany_ivan @dhana_bk @tonybambe @naranaia_ perjuangan teman” sampek nggak tidur, lembur, dengan waktu dan persiapan yang singkat juga video ini harus dibuat, semoga membuahkan hasil yang diharapkan kita semuanya, aamiin @fabienne_fng @rieckomara  @jemberfashioncarnaval @wdyaoktvian @rickyrijkaard @yusuf_isvania @natalia_fabsan @poppycapella_
